nodes.text: A Dairkan Starliner was a type of passenger liner that was in use around 7 ABY.

A notable example was the Jewel of Churba, which had accommodations for passengers to travel in unparalleled luxury on the starliner's upper decks. 
For example, a spiral docking port and shuttles were available to ultra-class passengers who wanted to avoid waiting to disembark with the other passengers.
